# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MYTH-CLI : Mission Critical Docker Exclusions
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Prevents context-copying that causes disk exhaustion.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Recursive Build & Runtime Targets
**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.log

# Global Repository Bloat
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
**/*~
**/*.swp

# Official Distribution Artifacts
**/*.whl
**/*.deb
**/*.snap
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.tgz

# Tactical & Sensitive Data (private key ONLY — myth.gpg is the PUBLIC key, needed in build context)
.aptly/
.cargo/
myth-private.key
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
notes/
logs/
config/.myth_history

# Environment files with potential secrets
.env
.env.*
.env.local

# Docs (large node_modules not needed for Docker)
docs/
